wikipedia_page.main: Alistair Law (born 12 February 1997) is an English YouTuber from Southampton. His videos feature parkour, with him climbing on a range of buildings and structures, as well as doing 'overnight challenges', where he and a group of friends attempt to stay in various commercial premises after closing hours.
